title: XIQ Access Point Status Detail
agents: special
catalog: hw/network
license: free
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check provides detailed status information for an ExtremeCloudIQ
 Access Point. The check reports:
  - Operational state
  - Network status (LAN / WAN / CAPWAP)
  - Firmware version
  - Serial number
  - Location information (LOC code)
  - BSSID per radio
 .
 The state is derived from:
  - OK: AP connected and operational
  - WARN: AP connected but degraded (missing radios, reduced service)
  - CRIT: AP disconnected or unreachable
  - UNKNOWN: Missing API fields or malformed data

item:
 The Access Point name as provided by XIQ.

perfdata:
 This check does not generate performance metrics.
